{"tid":1991344,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【思捷玩完】ESPRIT亞洲56店將全線結業","createTime":"2020-04-27T11:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T13:29:10.000Z","uid":22337,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"97571ec825dbb4216cfe0ab5086bd3c6a44f558a","tid":1991344,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"思捷環球（330）公佈，除了終止在中國大陸的業務外，思捷還決定關閉中國大陸以外在亞洲的所有56間零售店舖，尤其是新加坡、馬來西亞、台灣、香港及澳門。店舖關閉建議預期將於本財政年度末前完成。店舖關閉建議完成後，思捷將繼續中國的合資公司業務以及亞洲的批發業務和許可權業務，並專注於歐洲的核心市場。<br />\n<br />\n思捷表示，管理層正在制定一項重組計劃，而該計劃將於2020年6月底提交最近成立的債權人委員會以作批准。同時，該集團將繼續精簡其業務營運，藉以將成本及開支減至最少。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年3月底止9個月，該56間店舖為思捷收入帶來約2.67億元，佔集團同期總收入少於4%。<br />\n<br />\n根據思捷管理層的初步評估，估計店舖關閉建議將產生店舖關閉、資產和存貨減值及員工遣散費的一次性特殊成本，介乎於1.5億至2億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情入link睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200427/OUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200427%2FOUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4TUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=e1cdc417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200427%2FOUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU%2F&h=fb809645\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200427/OUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU/</a>"},{"pid":"f31611233e2251ca82f3c5a25e27beceaee0f63b","tid":1991344,"uid":89349,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:13:48.000Z","msg":"想當年係藍籌股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0RPeoc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0RPeoc.png&h=558c0799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被起底警務人員：警方資助更換車牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913997</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b079ed4d91015c68ca5290edf0940f66ff8d4fa6","tid":1991344